                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-9 col-md-8">
                <div class="comment">Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s.</div>
                <div class="author">Mary & Paul, Minesota got married june 26, 2014</div>
